messages.TRMSG_PRE_BATTLE:
Collecting electricity from the Valley
Windworks... That’s our mission.
messages.TRMSG_DEFEAT:
I really don’t like kids who also
happen to be tough Trainers...
messages.TRMSG_POST_BATTLE:
You don’t have an inkling of what
Team Galactic is trying to achieve!Of course, they don’t tell a grunt
like me anything, either... But still!
